text: Macrozamia longispina is a species of plant in the family Zamiaceae. It is endemic to Australia. ==References== longispina Category:Least concern biota of Queensland Category:Least concern flora of Australia Category:Nature Conservation Act rare biota Category:Rare flora of Australia Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by Paul Irwin Forster
